title: Ministry of Sound - The Annual 2014 (US Version) - 320 KBPS CBR
description:
Hey Guys!

I've been looking forever for the US Version of this album, when I realized no one has uploaded it yet I decided to throw in a few bucks and share it with the community. This is my thanks to all the awesome people here from whom I get all of my music from! Enjoy!

- AppRipper - Happy Hacking!

This the entire album from the US version of iTunes 320kbps CBR. The other country's version seem to watered down a bit with their selection of music. This one is great on the other hand, hope you enjoy!
